gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Magic 113, Bucks 88
gameRecap.excerpt: The Magic defeated the Bucks, 113-88. Paolo Banchero (26 points, 11 rebounds, seven assists) and Franz Wagner (25 points, five rebounds, three assists) led the Magic as Bobby Portis had 17 points and 10 rebounds for the Bucks. The Magic finish the season at 47-35 while the Bucks finish at 49-33.
